        <title>Normal Mail</title>
        <item>
            <title>1.0.15</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>What's new</h3>
<ul>
<li>Normal Mail can now be your default mail app. <code>mailto:</code> links from your browser, Calendar invites, and other apps will open a new compose window in Normal Mail with the address, subject, and body pre-filled.</li>
<li>A new "Default Mail App" section in Settings → General lets you set Normal Mail as the system default with one click.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
